      <!-- About Section -->
      <section class="section about-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
          <i class="section-icon bx bx-user"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-content">
          <p class="bio-text">
            I am <strong>Tony Cletus</strong>, a Builder deeply grounded in full-stack development, continuous learning,
            and exploring the unknown.
            I am the Founder and Program Manager at <strong>Programmify</strong>, a platform I started to give students
            the practical, hands-on experience I wished I had when starting out, which has now grown into a space where
            I build the builders of
            tomorrow.
            Beyond my startup experience, I am perpetually curious. I study AI model infrastructure, explore agentic
            engineering (regularly working with AI coding agents like Claude Code, OpenCode, Cursor, Antigravity, Qwen 3
            Coder, and Lovable), and constantly research new paradigms of intelligence. I am driven by an unending
            desire to build, I hate being bored, so I am always tinkering, trying, breaking, and learning.
          </p>
          <p class="bio-text" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            My roots are in Africa, and I am deeply passionate about identifying gaps where AI and technology can solve
            critical problems, even in regions with limited infrastructure. This drives my heavy research focus on
            projects like <strong>AANI</strong>.
            I value family, culture, and writing occasionally. In the past, I worked extensively as a marketer, giving
            me a unique edge in product growth.
            Looking toward the future, my curiosity extends to hardware, robotics, and even the universe and space
            exploration. I build independently with the hope that my research and creations will one day produce
            breakthroughs that change humanity, particularly for the Global South.
          </p>

          <p class="bio-text" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            Let's discuss collaborations! Feel free to <a href="mailto:tc@tonycletus.com" class="link-email">✉ contact
              me</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

